data.name: txtDirections.Text
data.value:
Aim the ball with your bat to clear blocks and enemies and earn points. The farther from the middle of your bat the ball hits, the sharper the angle when the ball bounces.
Clear all the blocks before time runs out to advance to the next level and earn an additional time bonus, but watch out! If you move too fast, you might miss the ball and lose a life. Enemies can also take away your lives with their bombs, so don't let your bat get hit!
High scores get rewarded; try your best to earn a spot on the leaderboard!
